תשובה:
```java
public static boolean isBalanced(int[] arr) {
int sum1 = 0;
int sum2 = 0;
int half = arr.length / 2;

for (int i = 0; i &lt; half; i++) {
sum1 += arr[i];
}

for (int i = half + 1; i &lt; arr.length; i++) {
sum2 += arr[i];
}

if (sum1 == sum2) {
return true;
}
return false;
}
```

